The reinforced connectors and thick cables inspire confidence that they will last for a long time, even with daily use or frequent bending.Moreover, the generous length of 10 feet allows for hassle-free connectivity even when using my devices at a distance from the power source. It brings convenience to my workspace or when I'm lounging on the couch, eliminating the need to sit close to a power outlet. I appreciate the two-pack inclusion, as it provides a spare cable that I can keep in my bag or use in another room.In terms of compatibility, these cables have proved to be compatible with a wide range of devices. From my Samsung smartphones to my Google Pixel devices, these cables work flawlessly, providing the necessary charging power without any compatibility issues.Overall, I highly recommend the [10ft 2-Pack] Long USB C to USB C Cable Fast Charging 60W, PD Type C Charger Cord Nylon. The fast charging performance, durable construction, and generous length make these cables an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable charging solution. Say goodbye to slow charging and flimsy cables – these cables deliver exceptional performance and are definitely worth every penny.I am extremely satisfied with my purchase, and I will certainly consider purchasing more from this brand in the future.
